data.value: The bright white light is blinding. Making it hard for you to see anything. Once the light fades away you look around to find yourself in a hospital bed. A few doctors walk into your room surprised to see you are awake. "We did not think you were ever gonna come to" one of them says. "What happened, how long have i been out?" you ask. "You have been in a coma for 120 days" replies the doctor. It all seems too real to be true but you are glad to have finally escaped the confines of your mind, but something seems off. You look outside the window and........
